        public boolean test(java.lang.StringBuilder s)
        This method will always fail if you pass a complete address line since it will look up the entire line. The recommended procedure is to pass in a string that is a good candidate to be a city name, remembering that many place names contain multiple words.
        Specified by:

        Parameters:
